MSI-USBN.description:
Description

The MSI-USBN device is a low-cost non-isolated USB-Serial converter. Its design exceptionally suited to integrate into larger solutions or mount into end-user devices.

MSI-485N.description:
Description

Preorder available, minimum quantity: 10pcs

The MSI-485N is a half-duplex differential bus transceiver / level shifter designated to use as OEM part in devices where communication in noisy environment over long distances is expected.

MSUSB-485N.description:
Description

The MSUSB-485N device is the non isolated USB-RS485 converter designed for use in cost efficient application for data acquisition and commissioning of RS-485 based systems.
